overview:
Satyak is an online technical support services to consumers and small businesses across a wide range of computing and communications devices and software.Founded in March 2012, Satyak Technical Services offers on-demand and brand-independent technical support service for computers, its Operating Systems, its software, and accessories. The best part is that it provides tech support for both in- and out-of- warranty products of any version even if their manufacturers had discontinued their development and support. Its support list includes almost each computer related brand.

Product Support List of Satyak includes desktops, laptops, netbooks, Windows OS, Office applications, Web Browsers, computer security applications (such as antivirus, firewall, Internet security, antispyware), external drives, MP3 Players, Digital Cameras, Scanners, Printers (inkjet, dot-matrix, laser, etc.), All-in-One devices, and so on. It services brands such as Dell, HP, Toshiba, Microsoft, Norton, Lenovo, McAfee, and AVG.
